cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for haze removal and assessment. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and visualization techniques, which makes cs.GR (Graphics) another likely category. The use of statistical metrics and machine learning techniques for assessment of haze removal algorithms suggests that cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) could also be relevant categories. Finally, the use of statistical analysis and optimization techniques for image processing suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) could also be a relevant category.
